/tools

This directory contains auxiliary tools for the project:
    * "gencom.sh", which is a Bash script used to prepend a common header to
      every single source file;
    * "mkdcmtk.sh", which is a Bash script used to reorganize a DCMTK
      distribution (fully Autotools-compliant);
    * "wxmsvc.sh", which is a Bash script used to cross-compile wxWidgets for
      Windows using Wine and the Microsoft Visual C++ compiler;
    * "xbuildwx.sh", which is a Bash script used to (cross-)compile wxWidgets
      for Windows using GCC.
